entry.title: Messy Buns - Synthetic Hair Scrunchies - Gray Hair Colors
entry.summary:
Vendor: Wholesale Princess
Type: Women, Girls - Hair Accessories
Price: 7.99

We all love the messy bun look, but actually creating it for yourself is no easy task... until now. With our messy bun hair scrunchies you can create the perfect messy bun in seconds. We have many colors available, just find your match and your can change your look in seconds. You'll love the natural-looking results, and how easy you can have that look with the messy bun hair scrunchie.

The synthetic hair bun on the scrunchie provides secure and comfortable attachment for all day wear and will give you a thicker, fuller ponytail or bun, with more volume. The elastic band prevents your hair from loosening and falling out of throughout the course of the day. It's the easiest way to create your own up-do at home.

These messy buns are perfectly suitable for any age. The hair scrunchie is easy to put on and fits nicely when used simultaneously with elastic hair ties.

entry.title: Baby Monthly Stickers - Nursery Toys
entry.summary:
Vendor: Wholesale Princess
Type: Baby - Monthly Stickers
Price: 6.99

These monthly stickers are the most fun, creative way to capture your baby's first year of life in photographs! Each month remove the relevant pre-cut sticker and use it as a photo prop on your little one's outfit, toy, blanket, or anything. Just peel, stick and click for adorable photos.

These also make the perfect baby shower gift for moms-to-be getting ready to celebrate a very special moment.
